snippet.title: Glitch Daddy: Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist at https://store.steampowered.com/app/2676440/Glitch_Daddy/

An abstract, psychedelic game by Sad Mask Party, the twisted brains behind Mango and The Lotus Holidays. 
A highly immersive and just slightly distorted tale of mystery, friendship, overcoming obstacles, romance, solitude and all around, love.
